title: Art Masterpieces of the National Gallery London (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Pdf / English / 1978 Crescent / 64 pages / 9.83 MB

The majestic Neo-Palladian facade of the National Gallery which graces the north side of London's Trafalgar Square is not only one of the city's best known 
landmarks, but also houses one of the world's greatest art collections. Indeed, for many visitors the National Gallery is one of the major attractions of this great capital city.
